org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.mxml

Interface IMXMLDeferredInstanceNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, IMXMLClassReferenceNode, IMXMLInstanceNode, IMXMLNode, ISourceLocation

    public interface IMXMLDeferredInstanceNode
extends IMXMLInstanceNode
    This AST node represents the instance of mx.core.DeferredInstanceFromClass or mx.core.DeferredInstanceFromFunction that the compiler implicitly creates as the value for a property or style of type mx.core.IDeferredInstance or mx.core.ITransientDeferredInstance.

    An IMXMLDeferredInstanceNode has exactly one child, which can be either an IMXMLClassNode (in the case of an DeferredInstanceFromClass) or an IMXMLInstanceNode (in the case of an DeferredInstanceFromFunction
